---
// src/pages/privacy-policy.astro
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy - WinBet"
  description="Learn about WinBet's privacy practices and how we protect your personal information."
>
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-yellow-500 mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>

    <section class="mb-8 text-lg text-white">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[#ffd700] mb-4">Introduction</h2>
      <p>
        At WinBet, we value your privacy and are committed to protecting your
        personal data. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and
        safeguard your information when you use our services. By accessing or
        using our platform, you consent to the practices described in this
        policy.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8 text-lg text-white">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[#ffd700] mb-4">
        Information We Collect
      </h2>
      <p>
        We collect personal information that you provide to us when you register
        for an account, make a deposit, or contact customer support. The
        information we collect may include:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
        <li>
          Personal details such as your name, email address, and phone number.
        </li>
        <li>
          Payment information (credit card details or cryptocurrency wallet
          addresses).
        </li>
        <li>
          Usage data, such as your IP address, browser type, and device
          information.
        </li>
        <li>
          Transaction history, including your deposit and withdrawal details.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8 text-lg text-white">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[#ffd700] mb-4">
        How We Use Your Information
      </h2>
      <p>
        The information we collect is used to provide, improve, and personalize
        our services. Specifically, we may use your information for:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
        <li>
          Verifying your identity and ensuring that you meet the eligibility
          requirements.
        </li>
        <li>Processing transactions such as deposits and withdrawals.</li>
        <li>Providing customer support and responding to your inquiries.</li>
        <li>
          Sending promotional communications, if you have opted in to receive
          them.
        </li>
        <li>
          Complying with legal obligations and preventing fraudulent activity.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8 text-lg text-white">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[#ffd700] mb-4">
        How We Protect Your Information
      </h2>
      <p>
        We implement a variety of security measures to protect your personal
        information. These measures include encryption, secure servers, and
        strict access controls. However, please note that no method of
        transmission over the Internet or method of electronic storage is 100%
        secure.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8 text-lg text-white">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[#ffd700] mb-4">
        Sharing Your Information
      </h2>
      <p>
        We do not sell or rent your personal information to third parties.
        However, we may share your information in the following cases:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
        <li>
          With third-party service providers who assist us in providing our
          services, such as payment processors and customer support services.
        </li>
        <li>
          If required by law, such as to comply with legal obligations or to
          protect our rights.
        </li>
        <li>
          With affiliates or partners in the event of a business transfer, such
          as a merger or acquisition.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8 text-lg text-white">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[#ffd700] mb-4">
        Your Rights and Choices
      </h2>
      <p>
        You have the right to access, update, or delete your personal
        information. If you wish to make any changes to your account or request
        the deletion of your personal data, you can contact us using the <a
          href="/support/contact"
          class="text-yellow-500">contact form</a
        >.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8 text-lg text-white">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[#ffd700] mb-4">Cookies</h2>
      <p>
        We use cookies and similar tracking technologies to enhance your
        experience on our platform. These technologies allow us to remember your
        preferences, analyze usage patterns, and deliver targeted
        advertisements. By using our services, you consent to the use of
        cookies.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8 text-lg text-white">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[#ffd700] mb-4">
        Changes to This Privacy Policy
      </h2>
      <p>
        We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. When we make
        changes, we will update the "last updated" date at the top of this page.
        We encourage you to review this policy periodically to stay informed
        about how we are protecting your information.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8 text-lg text-white">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[#ffd700] mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
      <p>
        If you have any questions or concerns about our privacy practices,
        please contact us via our <a
          href="/support/contact"
          class="text-yellow-500">contact form</a
        >.
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
